videos.headline: Rhyne Howard goes off in Kentucky's upset win over Georgia
videos.description: Rhyne Howard scores 30 points as she leads No. 21 Kentucky to take down No. 15 Georgia 84-76.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Highlight (Rhyne Howard goes off in Kentucky's upset win over Georgia) 2022/01/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howard's 30 points pushes Kentucky past Georgia
videos.description: No. 21 Kentucky records its first conference win with help from Rhyne Howard's 30 points in the 84-76 win over No. 15 Georgia.
